title: Frank Lloyd Wright Clock— Willits House
description:
Known for extending his architectural motifs into every aspect of home decor, Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867–1959) lent his vision to even the smallest of home furnishings. This beautifully crafted, hand-assembled desk clock with printed glass and solid wood case is inspired by his designs. Requires one AA battery (not included).

7 x 7 3/4 in.
